videos.description: J.P. Macura passes to an open Quentin Goodin who takes it to the rim for a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Macura connects with Goodin for dunk

videos.description: Justin Simon is left wide open and drills a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Simon drains 3 for St. John's

videos.description: Justin Simon finds an open lane to the rim for a strong two-handed jam while Xavier seems to be standing still on defense.
videos.headline: St. Johns capitalizes on slow Xavier defense

videos.description: Kaiser Gates dishes it out to an open J.P. Macura who knocks down a corner 3-pointer to fire up the bench.
videos.headline: Macura's 3 pumps up Xavier bench

videos.description: Naji Marshall jumps for a major slam but falls short.
videos.headline: Xavier's Marshall denied by rim

videos.description: St. John's Bashir Ahmed and Xavier's Tyrique Jones exchange words after the Red Storm loses 88-60 to the Musketeers.
videos.headline: Xavier and St. John's get chippy during postgame hand shakes
